{"tid":1609814,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"龍翔道有警察以手槍指向示威者，面露興奮笑容","createTime":"2019-10-01T15:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T05:05:42.000Z","uid":70063,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"39db643b25bc619f92021750b1a15b5fae772018","tid":1609814,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:33:43.000Z","msg":"有大批防暴警員突然衝向龍翔道，與示威者引起激烈衝突，期間一名警員叫另外的警員「開槍」，此時有警員掏出實彈手槍指向前方，面露興奮笑容，並配合警方防線後退。當時前方有多名包括本會在內的記者，並且傳出一下疑似實彈槍聲，未知是否已開槍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/423763107707890/posts/2374923975925117/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F423763107707890%2Fposts%2F2374923975925117%2F&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=ac12e097\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/423763107707890/posts/2374923975925117/</a>"},{"pid":"9605823729d25c1eadfd1367402faa5865f800fa","tid":1609814,"uid":65790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:37:19.000Z","msg":"狗撚線<br />\n成班魔鬼"},{"pid":"11d55b950552d78880e1ee07724a897455071e49","tid":1609814,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:38:16.000Z","msg":"10月2號-HKDI罷課行動 請其他IVE院校借鑑<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/egixgS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/egixgS</a>"},{"pid":"4ce106c983e6bed4a37a5438c82ead5444bcc8b3","tid":1609814,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:38:33.000Z","msg":"[緊急新戰線] 全民GIF圖賀佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/egkebS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/egkebS</a>"},{"pid":"4ebbf1d54aae31cecd7434cd239aff7894edcfba","tid":1609814,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1626d41a3f447f6d3ca8a8d1ac29a4aef52c9a89","tid":1609814,"uid":138051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:39:43.000Z","msg":"似係take咗嘢"},{"pid":"24534de14bfbc7f86ff6509e209067798abd0124","tid":1609814,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9605823729d25c1eadfd1367402faa5865f800fa","tid":1609814,"uid":65790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:37:19.000Z","msg":"狗撚線<br />\n成班魔鬼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:39:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/remove-all-powers-hong-kong-police-force-assist-establishment-temporary-militias-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fremove-all-powers-hong-kong-police-force-assist-establishment-temporary-militias-hong-kong&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=22bf99ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/remove-all-powers-hong-kong-police-force-assist-establishment-temporary-militias-hong-kong</a>"},{"pid":"4d3ce9c60c32fd41fb2aaf49c9beefee887ce5af","tid":1609814,"uid":218081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:39:55.000Z","msg":"解散警隊 殺人強姦 制度崩塌 刻不容緩"},{"pid":"52967abb1ac4f720ea4590a983f21a1d443bd97a","tid":1609814,"uid":45821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:40:46.000Z","msg":"有槍在手獸性就出哂來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1badd4eda73b65817ca5950d7cfb20b81e709c4","tid":1609814,"uid":279819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T05:05:42.000Z","msg":"【黑色10.1】龍翔道開槍片段曝光 便裝警實彈射幾十米外抗爭者<br />\n<br />\n警務處處長盧偉聰昨晚於記者會上表示，警方在油麻地、荃灣及黃大仙3個地點，都有警員使用警槍，總共開了6槍，包括荃灣向中五生開槍。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果讀者昨日在黃大仙龍翔道與沙田坳道交界，拍下警員開槍一幕，從讀者提供的片段所見，一批防暴警及便裝警員，在街頭拘捕兩名抗爭人士，當時場面混亂，其間有一名便裝警員首先拔槍，警員制服兩名抗爭人士便一同後退，有防暴警施放催淚彈掩護撤退，其間再有一名防暴警及一名便裝警員拔出佩槍，指向前面一批在遠處的抗爭人士，警員帶同被捕人士撤離期間，其中一名穿白色T恤便裝警員開了一槍。<br />\n讀者表示，看到一批警員突然衝出龍翔道，抗爭者四散逃走，警員制服兩人並按在地上，其後有警員拔槍指向抗爭人士，當時附近幾十米外都沒有人，之後警員在撤退期間無端開槍，聽到兩響槍聲，其中一下槍聲特別大，相信是實彈，另一下是催淚彈的聲響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191002/60106958\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60106958&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVjv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=69009c2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191002%2F60106958&h=7031b21a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20191002/60106958</a>"}]}